### 16. 退出登录 (需要登录)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
# {
#   "code": 1000,
#   "message": "success",
#   "data": null
# }

### 16. 上传用户头像 (需要登录)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

# {
#   "code": 1000,
#   "message": "success",
#   "data": "/api/file/avatar/user_3_1770028087.png"
# }

